title: NFL Roster Cuts: Dolphins ditch Josh Rosen, Washington releases Adrian Peterson (Football 9/5)
description:
It's a dreaded day for many around the NFL as teams must trim their rosters down to 53 players. That means a whole lot of cuts. To break down Saturday's notable moves, Will Brinson welcomes the Superfriends - Ryan Wilson and John Breech - for their reactions. 
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
